OL,3,CWho is DR Congo's 'statue' superfan
OL,4,Cand will he attend the next World Cup
OL,5,Cmatch?
OL,7,FA DR Congo superfan has gone viral
OL,8,Fonline for acting like a human statue
OL,9,Fduring World Cup matches.
OL,11,FMichel Nkuka Mboladinga, from the
OL,12,FDemocratic Republic of Congo, made his
OL,13,FWorld Cup debut at the DRC-Colombia
OL,14,Fmatch last week standing completely
OL,15,Fstill for the entire game.
OL,17,FKnown as Lumumba Vea, the superfan is
OL,18,Fknown for wearing red, yellow and blue
OL,19,Fsuits and ties and stands in one pose
OL,20,Fon a podium throughout the match.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
