PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782915513
OL,3,CWho is DR Congo's 'statue' superfan
OL,4,Cand will he attend the next World Cup
OL,5,Cmatch?
OL,7,FHis name and distinct style is based
OL,8,Fon the former Prime Minister of DR
OL,9,FCongo, Patrice Lumumba, and he has
OL,10,Fbecome somewhat of a mascot for the
OL,11,Fteam.
OL,13,FHowever, his World Cup travel plans
OL,14,Fhave come to a standstill.
OL,16,FHe has been denied a visa to the US so
OL,17,Fwill not be able to attend the
OL,18,Fknockout game between England and DR
OL,19,FCongo, in Atlanta.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782915513
OL,3,CWho is DR Congo's 'statue' superfan
OL,4,Cand will he attend the next World Cup
OL,5,Cmatch?
OL,7,FSo how will DR Congo cope without
OL,8,Ftheir statue superstar?
OL,10,FEnock Kabwende, dubbed "Lumumba
OL,11,FJunior", will fill in for the
OL,12,FCongolese icon.
OL,14,FSpeaking to the Telegraph, Yvette
OL,15,FKapinga Ngandu, DR Congo's ambassador
OL,16,Fto the US, said: "If Lumumba Vea
OL,17,Fcannot travel, then Lumumba Junior
OL,18,Fwill carry the torch in Atlanta.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
