PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782915513
OL,3,CWho is DR Congo's 'statue' superfan
OL,4,Cand will he attend the next World Cup
OL,5,Cmatch?
OL,7,F"Michel is the real one but junior is
OL,8,Fsmaller and a bit younger; he's the
OL,9,FGeneration Z fan."
OL,11,FHis senior is remaining positive and
OL,12,Fwas spotted celebrating and dancing in
OL,13,Fbars on Sunday after DR Congo
OL,14,Fqualified by winning 3-1 against
OL,15,FUzbekistan.
OL,17,FLumumba Vea became popular last year
OL,18,Fat the Africa World Cup of Nations and
OL,19,Fhas since gained fame at the World Cup.
OL,26,@qD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
