PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782915513
OL,3,CWho is DR Congo's 'statue' superfan
OL,4,Cand will he attend the next World Cup
OL,5,Cmatch?
OL,7,FHe was initially late to the
OL,8,Ftournament and missed DR Congo's
OL,9,Fopening match against Portugal, after
OL,10,Fquarantine restrictions were enforced
OL,11,Fdue to an Ebola outbreak in the
OL,12,Fcountry.
OL,14,FYet he managed to make the game
OL,15,Fagainst Colombia on 24 June, and since
OL,16,Fbecame an internet sensation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
