PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782915513
OL,3,CWho is DR Congo's 'statue' superfan
OL,4,Cand will he attend the next World Cup
OL,5,Cmatch?
OL,7,FHe has become a symbol and good luck
OL,8,Fcharm for the team, and fans from all
OL,9,Fover the world have copied his poses,
OL,10,Fdressing in a similar style and
OL,11,Fsaluting players.
OL,13,FLumumba Vea has said the poses
OL,14,Frepresent "unity", "resilience" and
OL,15,F"hope".
OL,17,FPosting on X the superfan said:
OL,18,F"Football is a passion. Football for
OL,19,FPeace and cohesion."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
