PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782915513
OL,3,CWho is DR Congo's 'statue' superfan
OL,4,Cand will he attend the next World Cup
OL,5,Cmatch?
OL,7,FHis style of mimicking the old DR
OL,8,FCongo prime minister reflects this.
OL,10,FPatrice Lumumba was an activist known
OL,11,Ffor helping to end Belgium's colonial
OL,12,Frule over Congo in 1960.
OL,14,FHe became the new DR Congo's first
OL,15,Fprime minister, but was assassinated
OL,16,Fwithin a year due to a conflict
OL,17,Fagainst a Belgian-backed independence
OL,18,Fmovement.
OL,20,FHe has since been recognised as a hero
OL,21,Fof independence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
