OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782915513
OL,3,CWho is DR Congo's 'statue' superfan
OL,4,Cand will he attend the next World Cup
OL,5,Cmatch?
OL,7,FLumumba Vea hasn't been so lucky
OL,8,Frecently with visa issues and a 1-0
OL,9,Floss to Colombia in Mexico, but
OL,10,FCongolese fans will likely be thinking
OL,11,Fof him as they face England in the
OL,12,Fknockout match on Wednesday night.
OL,14,FIf England win, DR Congo will be out
OL,15,Fof the tournament.
OL,17,FThe match kicks off at 5pm BST and
OL,18,Fwill be available to watch on the BBC.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
